{"tid":306568,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"比你會升職定保持現況","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T15:42:09.000Z","uid":73803,"like":22,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e885eb60be9f2b9b4589c2ae2224ca687b2720d","tid":306568,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"今日返工收到通知打算升我職，升senior sales,12k 升上15k底薪<br />\n但工作地點由旺角轉屯門，我就住大埔<br />\n平時返旺角就半個鐘，返屯門我估最快都1個鐘，仲要冇咁多返9個鐘，多數要十二碼<br />\n<br />\n比你地會點決定？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 升佢老母，多成3k <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 車錢都蝕，升都on9"},{"pid":"9a55b5df66c69994e00e71033980d99c74844737","tid":306568,"uid":87670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"升 捱一年 就轉工走"},{"pid":"4d5daddd23bb20a37a032f31c9472dfe41c8276a","tid":306568,"uid":92462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"9碼變12碼,返多左3分1,但人工無加到3分1喎,仲遠左時間同車錢"},{"pid":"9f1d29b478de946a5dfce24f3f4125b0bc0f0021","tid":306568,"uid":23392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"唔好只係睇短期利益咁短視 title同人工高左對轉工有用"},{"pid":"9b3a9d363fab08d66695da74197345ef62b6c7cd","tid":306568,"uid":1725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"一定升，為日後轉職增加籌碼"},{"pid":"a66ea6341077fc228add7ee0cc4907f6f15beaa9","tid":306568,"uid":92462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:36:08.000Z","msg":"問題個title係senior sales,senior到底有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d626ba216ff73c12cf0f623b85e615d80802dc1","tid":306568,"uid":35420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:13:11.000Z","msg":"升完再走"},{"pid":"189be2e436dadb4642f878c26e2f11f6c351c3d8","tid":306568,"uid":72173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"其實睇你接唔接受到<br />\n連工時同搭四你花多三四個鐘<br />\n但人工無跟比例加上去<br />\n<br />\n如果公司升你但居然咁大牌唔想升<br />\n可能下次又隔年幾兩年先升<br />\n<br />\n可以升完一兩個月轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11a932a8cde726e1917747e6438cccd91ec0b22","tid":306568,"uid":9758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T18:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9碼變12碼,返多左3分1,但人工無加到3分1喎,仲遠左時間同車錢</blockquote><br />\n你當返多咗個3分1係bonus/OT 多勞多得<br />\n咁樣諗會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c8c0b0960d4781ff46176c3fad5efcbfaafa3a","tid":306568,"uid":33058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:03:04.000Z","msg":"起碼比之後既臭閪hr知自己升過職"},{"pid":"d37ee6e7e3de0ecdfa17b783c7caadeb3724937b","tid":306568,"uid":8133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:11:18.000Z","msg":"升完就開始搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cfd38033969ce8b07f2ea52cfcee8542569435","tid":306568,"uid":73803,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:42:41.000Z","msg":"好，升佢老母試試水溫，唔掂就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2fcf2438a2b81791032fbeee68f2fdf36aac54","tid":306568,"uid":57313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"Promote完過兩星期咪走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對搵新工有好大幫助"},{"pid":"e4796a6afb50656c4dc1a8cdb69e9e78fabfdb4f","tid":306568,"uid":61586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"變相減薪"},{"pid":"027861aa75727ff8eeef383da581d2255b61bd9f","tid":306568,"uid":112483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"唔肯升會唔會好快比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05534d342f008e04038f2e598e4561bcb7b8378c","tid":306568,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔肯升會唔會好快比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會，個區經好睇我<br />\n因為上年讀緊書返PT,都同佢返每星期4-5日，聖誕新年都冇話唔交更，佢見我上個月轉做FT,先問我升唔升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我估出面其他公司都唔會話唔升就炒，最多之後有位都唔會升你，因為你都要有表現，做得好先會升你，咁就炒佢同玩尻公司同自己冇分別，你搞到鋪面冇左熟手唔夠人用，店長同區經嘈，區經又會打返上去office 嘈，最後office 又會搵返果個HR <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480b51c5fe897e8b9bac5521d71c4150d12339bf","tid":306568,"uid":73803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"岩岩收工收到通知，下個月會升，遲下會出notes <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為始終都係第一次升職，我今年先20歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以好多謝各位巴絲打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}